== Famous people from Sumy ==
*[[Karl Burman]] (1882<U+2013>1965), Estonian architect; was born in Sumy
*[[Lev Yefimovitch Kerbel]], Soviet sculptor
*[[Oleh Husyev]] (born 1983), Ukrainian football player
*[[Ekaterina Tsibulskaya]], polyglot, traveller, philosopher, historian
*[[Bogdan Titomir]]{{citation needed|date=September 2011}} (born 1967), Russian musician, rapper and DJ
*[[Viktor Yushchenko]] (born 1954), President of Ukraine

